Create a web application using HTML, Javascript for a billing system.

Input values will be item name, quantity, price of single item. There will be two buttons add and bill.
After clicking the add button the items should be stored in local storage of the browser and should be displayed in a tabular format.
After clicking the bill button total price should be displayed.

Note: If the above tasks are achieved then you can beautify the web application using CSS which will be awarded extra points
